title: Straame Pack of 12 or 24 Black Safety Work Gloves, Outdoors PU and Nylon Non-Slip Work Handling Gloves, Good Dexterity Firm Grip Protective Working Gloves Size (Pack of 12 Pair's, S)
features: WORK GLOVES: Perfect for every material handing product work. Thanks to their non-slip coated material, these working gloves are suitable for carrying rough and bulky objects in a high range of applications such as builders, construction, warehouse, mechanic or even gardening, grabbing bricklaying tools or any other function that needs a firm grip.

PU COATED NYLON: Made of polyurethane and coated nylon, a lightweight, resistant, and flexible fabric, these safety gloves ensure the feeling of the object held. They will keep your hands protected all year round. Comfortable winter work gloves that will keep your hands warm and protected while working outdoors.
SAFETY WORK GLOVES: Protective gloves with high freedom of movement and flexibility for a great tactile feel. Ideal for work outdoors. Dexterity guaranteed.

LARGE SIZE RANGE: Our work gloves are sold in packs of 12 and 24. Suitable work gloves men and women as a big selection of sizes are provided: XS (7) to XL (11). Each gloves size has a different cuff colour. Designed to fit the palm perfectly.
FRICTION PROTECTED: These gloves will protect your skin when lifting and carrying heavy rough materials. The weight of the object would feel easier to lift and your grip strength won't be affected.
